'''Milworm''', also known as the '''Marcus the Worm''', is an [[Special:MyLanguage/Avatar Marketplace|Avatar Marketplace]] avatar & [[Special:MyLanguage/Public Avatars|public avatar]] in [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat|VRChat]]. The character originated as an internet meme within VRChat in early 2025, when Twitch streamer [https://www.twitch.tv/jouffa Jouffa] portrayed it with a custom worm avatar and a distinctive text-to-speech voice. Official marketing has featured the character alongside content creators Roflgator and Jouffa.

